data.description: NEW PRICE! Location, location, location!  It may sound cliché but I promise you won't care when you see how truly amazing this location in Cahaba Heights is!  You are walking distance from the elementary school and the entertainment district with restaurants, shopping, Starbucks and more!  This traditional, ranch style home is situated on a large, corner lot and offers ample parking space in the newly poured driveway and lots of entertaining space in the fenced backyard with new, oversized patio area.  Inside you will find original hardwood flooring through all living areas and tile/marble in the bathrooms.  The kitchen was completely updated and is so bright and open that it will quickly become your favorite room in the house!  The living room is quaint and cozy and features a real, wood-burning fireplace.  All 3 bedrooms are down the hall with the owner suite privately tucked in the back of the house.  Make this gem your new home today!
